Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}打破了原有的安靜祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}無所顧忌地大肆爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不給對方以喘息的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不給彼此以留下的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:39.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我一直喜愛你凝視我的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:47.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也始終懷念你帶給我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那時整個世界只有我們二人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那時我們二人就是整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:01.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我還是會像過去一樣顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:09.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我還是會為你放棄所有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:17.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我還是會像過去一樣顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:25.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}只是為你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:32.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}We broke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Everything that was right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}We both enjoyed a good fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And we solved
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}All the holes we had to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}To make the other one leave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:39.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I loved the way you looked at me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:47.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I miss the way you made me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}When we were alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}When we were alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:01.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll shiver like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:09.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll leave him just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:17.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll shiver like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:25.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:32.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Like I used to
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚冬之山林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若傳來低沉微弱 如細語之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,則不久後 春蟲將齊齊轉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此為眾山之靈商議甦醒日期的響動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:33.38,title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)\p1\pos(1104,499)\c&H353664&}m 0 0 l -500 0 l -500 100 l 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:33.38,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)\pos(1091,302)}冬之底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下頭疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想在驚蟄之前離開這條光脈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來今年比預想的早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚蟄之後的蟲大抵饑餓 很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然來信叫我了 但是眼下也沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不是什麼急事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先避幾天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天還冷著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 醒來之後就是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜得不太尋常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪早就該化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連颪笛都還在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然已經沒有隆冬時的威力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對面那座山已經沒有雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為那邊向陽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颪笛在遷徙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們正在北歸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座山上的颪笛群還沒跟牠們匯合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直在往下走 怎麼又繞回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山封閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進山的時候沒感覺到什麼異常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬蟲無法遷徙也是因為這個緣故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見見山靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點聲音都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葎蟲的氣息也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}註：這種蟲棲息在土中 類似山的神經
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光酒把山靈叫出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 都不知道發生了什麼 還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的山靈…找到沼澤就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能老老實實地找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說山靈了 連隻動物都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過仔細看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是到處都有山崩的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是秋天遭了颱風吧 還是挺厲害的颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山靈為了療傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便封閉了山 讓整座山冬眠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 對衰弱的生物而言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬眠可能讓牠們直接死去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對面那座山已經是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這裡卻還沒有復甦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說這座山只能等死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這麼下去我也會被牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才有東西在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水面沒有上凍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 喂 山靈閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把山封閉到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面早就是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 牠們聚集起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝著這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個沼澤怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有底嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在泥裡 但是卻能夠呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們都睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光酒在不斷湧出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在這裡療傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山還沒有死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天…到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颪笛還在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們遷徙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山開放了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死 這下子蟲煙也全報廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來得比想像中輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為山還沒完全復原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是山靈替我抑制了蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過連光酒都沒了真是損失慘重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 衰弱的颪笛如果想要遷徙 光酒確實是必要的養分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我進山…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了搞到光酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都在山靈大人的掌控之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟春回大地了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬已去 山含笑 地似錦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 棘之道
